00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:57.680 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Eight to 10 feet?

00:10:57.680 --> 00:10:59.805 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTIN: Researchers at
the Institute of HeartMath

00:10:59.805 --> 00:11:01.397 align:middle line:84%
will stand behind
three to four feet.

00:11:01.397 --> 00:11:03.230 align:middle line:84%
But nonetheless, we're
producing this field.

00:11:03.230 --> 00:11:04.250 align:middle line:90%
So right now, our fields--

00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:05.542 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Are intermingling, yes.

00:11:05.542 --> 00:11:07.790 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTIN: You and I are
commingling right now.

00:11:07.790 --> 00:11:10.880 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So when you come into
a room with your loved ones,

00:11:10.880 --> 00:11:15.480 align:middle line:84%
