intermingle before you actually

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:16.280 align:middle line:90%
do.

00:11:16.280 --> 00:11:18.087 align:middle line:90%
Or if you're in--

00:11:18.087 --> 00:11:19.170 align:middle line:90%
that makes a lot of sense.

00:11:19.170 --> 00:11:20.600 align:middle line:84%
So if you're a work
environment and you

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:22.100 align:middle line:84%
come into the field
of someone who's

00:11:22.100 --> 00:11:24.080 align:middle line:84%
maybe having anxiety
or stress, you

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:25.920 align:middle line:84%
