walk into the room.

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:26.900 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: You very possibly can.

00:11:26.900 --> 00:11:28.460 align:middle line:84%
This may be one
way to explain it.

00:11:28.460 --> 00:11:30.380 align:middle line:84%
What's interesting
is that the energy

00:11:30.380 --> 00:11:32.690 align:middle line:84%
in the field, the
frequencies or the radio

00:11:32.690 --> 00:11:35.420 align:middle line:84%
stations in the field, do
change depending upon what

00:11:35.420 --> 00:11:36.950 align:middle line:90%
we're feeling emotionally.

00:11:36.950 --> 00:11:40.610 align:middle line:84%
If we're experiencing a strong
negative emotion, for example,

00:11:40.610 --> 00:11:42.517 align:middle line:84%
like frustration
or anger, it will

00:11:42.517 --> 00:11:44.350 align:middle line:84%
produce what's called
an incoherent spectra,

00:11:44.350 --> 00:11:45.892 align:middle line:84%
a lot of frequencies,
but they're not

00:11:45.892 --> 00:11:47.540 align:middle line:90%
working harmoniously.

00:11:47.540 --> 00:11:51.260 align:middle line:84%
If we are experiencing, for
example, a feeling of gratitude

00:11:51.260 --> 00:11:53.300 align:middle line:84%
and it was sincere or
a feeling of care that

00:11:53.300 --> 00:11:55.820 align:middle line:84%
was really genuine,
then the field changes.

00:11:55.820 --> 00:11:58.790 align:middle line:84%
We produce more of what's
called a harmonic spectra.

00:11:58.790 --> 00:12:01.483 align:middle line:90%
So there's harmony in the field.

00:12:01.483 --> 00:12:03.150 align:middle line:84%
And we're sending
this out all the time.

00:12:03.150 --> 00:12:04.525 align:middle line:84%
So in a sense,
through out heart,

00:12:04.525 --> 00:12:06.560 align:middle line:90%
we're broadcasting our emotions.

00:12:06.560 --> 00:12:09.350 align:middle line:84%
Now this is where the inquiry
gets interesting to me.

00:12:09.350 --> 00:12:12.050 align:middle line:84%
Because now we go beyond
biology and we're into physics.

00:12:12.050 --> 00:12:14.750 align:middle line:84%
How does my field relate
to the field in my brain?

00:12:14.750 --> 00:12:16.190 align:middle line:84%
How does my field
and your field,

00:12:16.190 --> 00:12:19.130 align:middle line:84%
how are we relating now
at an energetic level?

00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:22.280 align:middle line:84%
Beyond that, how does the
collective field of humanity

00:12:22.280 --> 00:12:23.390 align:middle line:90%
relate?

00:12:23.390 --> 00:12:25.550 align:middle line:84%
And then how does the
collective field of humanity

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:29.450 align:middle line:84%
relate to the fields that
the Earth naturally produces?

00:12:29.450 --> 00:12:33.740 align:middle line:84%
Like the gentleman who sent us
a message earlier about he's

00:12:33.740 --> 00:12:35.960 align:middle line:84%
working twice as
many hours, his job's

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:37.665 align:middle line:84%
in jeopardy, whatever
those things are,

00:12:37.665 --> 00:12:38.540 align:middle line:90%
those are big things.

00:12:38.540 --> 00:12:40.207 align:middle line:84%
And I have understanding
and compassion.

00:12:40.207 --> 00:12:41.200 align:middle line:90%
They are stressful.

00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:43.490 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not saying, you just
do a heart technique and, poof,

